definitions.definition: A town and civil parish in Windsor and Maidenhead , Berkshire , England ( OS grid ref SU965775 ) .
Ellipsis of Eton College , a prestigious public school for boys in Eton .
A town in Murray County , Georgia , United States .
A habitational surname from Old English .
